item.description:
Time for another outdoor incubator.

This time we are heading into the dark realms of Cambridge forest, aka the Cambridge Common.

We will meetup at the corner of Garden St. and Mass Ave. There are some stone benches there marking the entrance way to the common. Can't miss it.

I'll have another fun round of improv games planned out. If there are any requests for games or something you'd like to work on in particular this week i.e. scene work, characters, spontaneity, etc. just email me and let me know.

Hope to see you all there in sunshine and the shade.

Rock on!

Jason J.
item.how_to_find_us: I'll look like me! Oo maybe I'll even make a sign!
item.name: Cambridge Improv's Incubator Vacation...
